latestReleaseNotes:
### Release info
Purple A11y is available as a desktop app for Mac and Windows. The setup files can be downloaded under `Assets` at the bottom of the page.

### Installation Guide
* Refer to the [Installation Guide](https://github.com/GovTechSG/purple-a11y-desktop/blob/master/INSTALLATION.md) for Windows and Mac.

### What's New
#### Features
- Support large scan by increasing heap memory to 6GB limit when using npm run cli and npm run start and here

#### Improvements
- Reduces error when crawler encounter non-HTML document
- Reduce error verbosity when MIME check falls
- More robust handling of redirected URLs
- Preparation for rename to Oobee
latestPreReleaseNotes:

Purple A11y is available as a desktop app for Mac and Windows. The setup files can be downloaded under `Assets` at the bottom of the page.
